OpenEmbedded/Yocto BSP layer for Blue Chip Technology's i.MX6 based platforms
=============================================================================

This layer provides support for Blue Chip Technology's i.MX6 based platforms
for use with OpenEmbedded and/or Yocto Freescale's BSP layer.

Supported boards are Blue Chip Technology's RE3 and RM3 (collectively known as Rx3)

This layer depends on:

URI: git://git.openembedded.org/openembedded-core
branch: krogoth
revision: HEAD

URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/meta-fsl-arm
branch: krogoth
revision: HEAD

Contributing
------------

To contribute to this layer you should the patches for review to the
maintainer.

    dchirgwin@bluechiptechnology.co.uk

Source code:

    https://github.com/bluechiptechnology/meta-bct-rx3

